snippet.textDisplay: It seems every year Coke Studio now needs a dead celebrity singer to churn out an emotional tribute. Last year's Rang was a major win as the late and great Amjad Sabri was in it. This song, however, misses the mark, made no easier by the fact that nothing can do justice to the late and great JJ's voice. Also, season 10 being a damp squib in general, feeling underwhelmed by this good-intentioned tribute is only natural. Thanks but no thanks, Choke Studio.
snippet.textOriginal: It seems every year Coke Studio now needs a dead celebrity singer to churn out an emotional tribute. Last year's Rang was a major win as the late and great Amjad Sabri was in it. This song, however, misses the mark, made no easier by the fact that nothing can do justice to the late and great JJ's voice. Also, season 10 being a damp squib in general, feeling underwhelmed by this good-intentioned tribute is only natural. Thanks but no thanks, Choke Studio.
